    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1586370/extras/02208c6d080c677983a50500dfe6d1be.webp?t=1634525362\" width=600 height=63 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1586370/extras/4cb4d0128c207d028d58286be233df0a.avif?t=1634525362\" width=600 height=210 /></span><br>Anopek is a groundbreaking mashup of genres, mixing shooter and metroidvania elements, with a stylized look right from the consoles of your childhood.<br><br>Begin your journey to a dying planet and discover the relics of the past. Reconnect with the ancient lore, and explore the labyrinthine temple grounds to learn it’s secrets.<br><br>Unlock a variety of weapons with unique abilities to aid your exploration, allowing you to delve deeper into the mysteries of the past, and empower yourself with ancient relics.<br><br>Seek out and challenge the pantheon of gods to reclaim the lost parts of your soul. Battle horrifying monsters and duel the divine to prove yourself worthy.<br><br>Fulfill the ancient prophecy that Anopek has foretold…<br><br>Or deny it, and choose your own path.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1586370/extras/9259732d0b690034ceedc3cc9d2904c4.webp?t=1634525362\" width=600 height=63 /></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1586370/extras/02208c6d080c677983a50500dfe6d1be.webp?t=1634525362\" width=600 height=63 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1586370/extras/8eb4a35b842a49a2423e9cf19199a76e.avif?t=1634525362\" width=600 height=210 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Retro shooter sensibilities coupled with traditional metroidvania action.<br></li><li>Blast your way through a variety of monsters and enemies.<br></li><li>Defeat clever and difficult bosses!<br></li><li>Explore a massive tomb resplendent with many different areas ranging from ancient tombs to flying temples!<br></li><li>Features an amazing and dynamic soundtrack, one of the most important staples of exploration.<br></li><li>Unlock unique weapons to combat the creatures you have awoken.<br></li><li>Use abilities to explore the temple, unlocking new areas with unique aesthetics.<br></li><li>Support for key rebinding and modern controllers. Change the game to play using only a keyboard, just like retro shooters! Or, use it for enhanced accessibility.<br></li><li>After completing the game, seek out the Gauntlet of the Gods for an additional challenge!<br></li><li>For further replayability, enable the “Mirror Mode” option in the game for a unique perspective.<br></li><li>Manual included with concept art!</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1586370/extras/9259732d0b690034ceedc3cc9d2904c4.webp?t=1634525362\" width=600 height=63 /></span>",
